&lt;a href=&quot;http://henning.kropponline.de/2015/10/04/distcp-between-kerberized-and-none-kerberized-cluster/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://henning.kropponline.de/2015/10/04/distcp-between-kerberized-and-none-kerberized-cluster/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
